name: Squid vs Jelly Fish
description:
Explore a surreal underwater environment as a giant squid. Watch out for dangerous jelly fish -- join up with friendly squid to fight them off.  

Friendly squid will automatically attack nearby enemies. The player character does not attack, but the other squid will follow and protect. 

Destroy all jelly fish or simply take a relaxing swim in the ocean -- the choice is yours. 

Created for the Brackeys 2021 Game Jam with theme "Stronger Together."
